        hinglish: ['Innā naḥnu nazzalnā <b>adh-dhikra</b> wa-innā lahū laḥāfiẓūna - Beshak humne hi is <b>zikr</b> ko nazil kiya hai aur hum hi iski hifazat karne wale hain.', 'Fas’alū ahla <b>adh-dhikri</b> in kuntum lā taʿlamūna - Toh agar tum nahi jaante toh <b>ilm</b> walon se pooch lo.']
