        hinglish: ['Allāhu <b>nūru</b> as-samāwāti wal-arḍi - Allah aasmanon aur zameen ka <b>noor</b> hai.', 'Yurīdūna liyuṭfi’ū <b>nūra</b> Allāhi bi-afwāhihim - Woh chahte hain ke Allah ke <b>noor</b> ko apne muhon se bujha dein.']
