        hinglish: ['Ini <b>l-ḥukmu</b> illā lillāhi - <b>Hukm</b> sirf Allah hi ka hai.', 'Alaysa Allāhu bi-aḥkami <b>al-ḥākimīna</b> - Kya Allah sab <b>haakimon</b> se bada haakim nahi hai?']
